{"tid":265092,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【終極睇淡】辛格爾：鬼門關已開！轉揸現金為上策","createTime":"2017-05-31T11:27:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T09:00:19.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d0019f2cf84f1ed5d7ab073878926c1c04c7205","tid":265092,"uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T11:27:37.000Z","msg":"【新增影片】<br />\n<br />\n億萬富豪及著名投資者辛格爾（Paul Singer）睇淡美國經濟與股市前景，本月初24小時內籌措50億美元（約390億港元），卻沒有再投資股市，而是未雨綢繆，認為轉揸現金為上策。<br />\n<br />\n72歲的辛格爾在最新的致投資者的信指出，美股和美債的低波動性持續，但他大膽預測美股面臨大跌市。辛格爾估計美國總統特朗普的經濟刺激方案，未必獲國會順利通過。此外，儲局的無限量寬措施對市場的功效漸失，美國經濟無可避免步入一個短暫衰退期，現刻市況猶如「鬼門關」已經打開。<br />\n<br />\n截至今年4月1日止，辛格爾管理對沖基金旗下總資產約330億美元。路透報道，辛格爾本月初曾於24小時內極速籌措50億美元資金。不過，該筆資金沒有用來再投資或炒股，辛格爾認為「現金為王」，目前是盡儲「子彈」好機會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170531/large/1496212324_3255.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170531%2Flarge%2F1496212324_3255.jpg&h=62275a68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n著名投資者辛格爾（Paul Singer）睇淡美國經濟與股市前景，籲轉揸現金。(路透社網站圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56764580&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170531\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56764580%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170531&d=UKJ7iNP0vuxfX4FTDXyrgdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=40beaeb9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56764580%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170531&h=00808264\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56764580&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170531</a>"},{"pid":"92d487202c90495f917de8f8dfcf63f5b4faf912","tid":265092,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T14:11:09.000Z","msg":"其實係唔係第二個2007年，明知係泡沬都要跟住炒<img 